      "stage": "Design",
      "set_the_stage": "Now we design the thinking of the agent, on the board, before we open Colab. We'll walk through all three agents one at a time: what goes in, what happens inside, why each choice is made, and what to watch out for.\n\nFor each agent you'll see its shape drawn out, then the steps inside it, then the reasoning, then the one thing that must never break. By the end of this session, you can draw the whole solution yourself.\n\nThe build session next won't teach you anything new; it just makes this design run. Design it clearly here, and the code becomes the easy part.",
