      "set_the_stage": "Now I'll build the real thing in front of you, live, in a Google Colab notebook, running it step by step on the actual 25 resumes. I'm using the paid demo key so it never stalls while you're watching.\n\nWatch me narrate every cell back to the design on the board: this cell is Agent 1 extracting, this cell is Agent 2 judging, this one drafts for the human. The code should feel like the obvious transcription of a design you already understand.\n\nAt the end we close the loop on trust: we compare the agent's top 5 to the top 5 you picked by hand yesterday. Where they agree, where they differ, and why.",
